# Studio Ghibli Films CLI 

This application was created to give the user more information about 
the wonderful animated films of Studio Ghibli, using a command line interface. This application allows the user 
view a list of all 20 films and select a particilar film to learn more.

## Installation

Clone the repository with 
git clone git@github.com:ecastille924/ghibli_cli.git

## Usage

Execute the the bin file './bin/run' 
You will be shown a numbered list of films.
Enter the number corresponding to the fil you'd like to know about.
You will be shown a synopsis, learn who directed & produced the film, the year it was released, and the 
ever-important Rotten Tomatoes score. 

